name: Vaiana / Moana
description:
Please contact me here on civitAi or on Twitter if you want to provide the LoRa in a generation service.

TLDR (Because I don't care)

Use vaiana <lora:vaiana_v10:1> in positiv promt.

If you like the LoRa, please feel free to share your generated images here and leave a review (or at least a rating) ;D

About

Here comes Vaiana (Based on the distribution market it can also be Moana, didn't know that until now xD), make way, make way... uuuh

Okay well, another one of my nonRL girl experiments. Now I have a LoRa and a catchy song stuck in my head. ._.

Training

I might do a v2 where I replace some pics with the outfits from the second "wreck it ralph" movie, because the current version is very biased towards Vaiana's red "top" (So, any kind of variaty might be an improvement for the model).

Usage

No weighing is required, so it's as simple as that:

vaiana <lora:vaiana_v10:1>

It heavily depends on the Checkpoint you are using which sampler should be used.
